<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Stamina & Turn Economy - Untamed</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<nav class="nav">
			<div class="container">
				<a href="/" class="logo">UNTAMED</a>
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/rules">Rules</a>
					<a href="/quick-reference">Quick Reference</a>
					<a href="/character">Characters</a>
					<a href="/bestiary">Bestiary</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<main>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="breadcrumb">
					<a href="/rules">‚Üê Back to Rules</a>
				</div>

				<header class="page-header">
					<h1>Stamina & Turn Economy</h1>
					<p class="subtitle">The lifeblood of combat</p>
				</header>

				<article class="content">
					<!-- Core Philosophy -->
					<section class="rule-section highlight">
						<h2>1Ô∏è‚É£ Core Philosophy: Stamina Is Tempo</h2>
						<p>In Untamed:</p>
						<ul class="key-points">
							<li><strong>Stamina represents breath, footing, balance, and combat rhythm.</strong></li>
							<li>It is <strong>not mana</strong>.</li>
							<li>It is <strong>not optional</strong>.</li>
							<li>Running out is <strong>dangerous</strong>.</li>
							<li>Forcing stamina loss is a <strong>valid strategy</strong>.</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="callout">
							<strong>Combat is not about trading HP.</strong> It is about controlling exhaustion. When stamina collapses, fights end.
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Combat Structure -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>2Ô∏è‚É£ Combat Structure</h2>
						<h3>Rounds</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Each round represents <strong>~6 seconds</strong>.</li>
							<li>Combat proceeds in <strong>Initiative order</strong>.</li>
							<li><strong>Initiative = d20 + DEX modifier.</strong></li>
							<li>Ties ‚Üí higher INS acts first.</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<!-- On Your Turn -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>3Ô∏è‚É£ On Your Turn</h2>
						<p>On your turn, you may:</p>

						<div class="action-block move">
							<h3>üü¢ Move</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Move up to your base Move Speed (30 ft default).</li>
								<li>Moving within base speed costs <strong>0 Stamina</strong>.</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="action-block action">
							<h3>üîµ Action</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Attack</li>
								<li>Use a Technique</li>
								<li>Set a trap</li>
								<li>Interact meaningfully with environment</li>
								<li>Most Actions cost <strong>1 Stamina</strong> unless specified otherwise.</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="action-block fast">
							<h3>üü° Fast Action</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Minor quick task (drink tonic, swap weapon, trigger ability)</li>
								<li><strong>Maximum 1 per turn</strong></li>
								<li>Costs Stamina only if specified</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="action-block prep">
							<h3>üü£ Preparation (Replaces Action)</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Costs <strong>0 Stamina</strong></li>
								<li>Sets up a benefit for next turn or reaction</li>
								<li>If damaged: CON save DC 10 or lose Preparation</li>
								<li>You may move up to base speed while preparing</li>
								<li>Sprinting cancels Preparation</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="action-block reaction">
							<h3>‚ö™ Reaction (1 per round)</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Triggered outside your turn</li>
								<li>Costs <strong>1 Stamina</strong> unless specified</li>
								<li><strong>You cannot React if:</strong>
									<ul>
										<li>Stunned</li>
										<li>Paralyzed</li>
										<li>Restrained (unless feature says otherwise)</li>
									</ul>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Stamina Rules -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>4Ô∏è‚É£ Stamina Rules</h2>

						<h3>Starting Stamina</h3>
						<div class="formula">
							<strong>6 + CON modifier</strong> (minimum 1)
						</div>
						<p class="note">This is the canonical formula. Lock this. Do not change elsewhere.</p>

						<h3>Stamina Costs</h3>
						<table class="cost-table">
							<thead>
								<tr>
									<th>Action</th>
									<th>Cost</th>
								</tr>
							</thead>
							<tbody>
								<tr>
									<td>Basic Attack</td>
									<td>1 STA</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Most Techniques</td>
									<td>1+ STA (as listed)</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Dodge</td>
									<td>1 STA</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Block</td>
									<td>1 STA</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Parry</td>
									<td>1 STA</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Sprint (per 10 ft beyond base)</td>
									<td>1 STA</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>Stand from Prone</td>
									<td>2 STA</td>
								</tr>
							</tbody>
						</table>

						<h3>Sprinting</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>You may exceed base movement.</li>
							<li>For every 10 ft beyond base speed: Pay <strong>1 Stamina</strong>.</li>
							<li>Difficult terrain counts as double movement before sprint calculation.</li>
							<li>Climbing or swimming may require Sprint cost at GM discretion.</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<!-- End of Turn Recovery -->
					<section class="rule-section highlight">
						<h2>5Ô∏è‚É£ End of Turn Recovery</h2>
						<p>You regain stamina based on your choices.</p>

						<div class="recovery-box">
							<h3>Standard Turn (You spent stamina)</h3>
							<p>‚Üí No automatic recovery.</p>
						</div>

						<div class="recovery-box breathing">
							<h3>Controlled Turn (No Action AND No Fast Action taken)</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>You may move up to base speed.</li>
								<li>You may <strong>NOT</strong> Sprint.</li>
								<li>At end of turn: <strong>Regain 4 Stamina</strong>.</li>
							</ul>
							<p class="note">This is called a <strong>Breathing Turn</strong>. Breathing Turns are intentional tactical resets.</p>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Short Rest -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>6Ô∏è‚É£ Short Rest</h2>
						<p><strong>~10 minutes of downtime.</strong></p>
						<ul>
							<li>Restore Stamina to full.</li>
							<li>Remove Exhausted condition (if not reduced to 0 HP).</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<!-- Exhaustion State -->
					<section class="rule-section danger">
						<h2>7Ô∏è‚É£ Exhaustion State (0 Stamina)</h2>
						<p>If you reach 0 Stamina:</p>
						<div class="callout danger">
							<strong>You gain the Exhausted condition.</strong>
						</div>

						<h3>Exhausted:</h3>
						<ul class="danger-list">
							<li>Stamina is set to 0.</li>
							<li>You <strong>cannot take Actions</strong>.</li>
							<li>You <strong>cannot take Fast Actions</strong>.</li>
							<li>Movement is <strong>halved</strong>.</li>
							<li>Attacks against you have <strong>advantage</strong>.</li>
							<li>You <strong>automatically fail STR and DEX saves</strong>.</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>On your next turn:</h3>
						<p>If you take no Action:</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Regain 4 Stamina at end of turn.</li>
							<li>Exhausted ends.</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="callout">
							<strong>Exhaustion is not death.</strong> It is collapse.
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Monster Stamina -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>8Ô∏è‚É£ Monster Stamina (Unified Rule)</h2>
						<p>Monsters follow the same stamina structure:</p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Stamina = 10 + CON score.</strong></li>
							<li>They spend stamina on attacks and abilities.</li>
							<li><strong>When monsters reach 0 Stamina:</strong>
								<ul>
									<li>They lose access to Signature Moves.</li>
									<li>Movement is reduced by half.</li>
									<li>They may trigger collapse behavior (if listed).</li>
								</ul>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="callout">
							<strong>Monsters do not ignore stamina.</strong> They obey the same physics.
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Action Economy Constraints -->
					<section class="rule-section">
						<h2>9Ô∏è‚É£ Action Economy Constraints</h2>
						<h3>Hard Limits:</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>1 Action</strong> per turn.</li>
							<li><strong>1 Fast Action</strong> per turn.</li>
							<li><strong>1 Reaction</strong> per round.</li>
							<li>Cannot stack multiple Preparations.</li>
							<li>Cannot chain Fast Actions.</li>
							<li><strong>Monsters are allowed more actions</strong> depending on their tier.</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="note">This keeps stamina meaningful.</p>
					</section>

					<!-- The Combat Rhythm -->
					<section class="rule-section highlight">
						<h2>üîü The Combat Rhythm (Table Reminder)</h2>
						<p>Combat alternates between:</p>
						<ul class="rhythm-list">
							<li><strong>Pressure Turns</strong> (spending stamina)</li>
							<li><strong>Breathing Turns</strong> (recovering stamina)</li>
							<li><strong>Collapse States</strong> (Exhaustion)</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="callout">
							<p><strong>If players never feel pressure</strong>, stamina costs are too low.</p>
							<p><strong>If players never need Breathing Turns</strong>, monsters are too weak.</p>
							<p><strong>If players collapse every fight</strong>, stamina costs are too high.</p>
						</div>
					</section>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>

		<style>
			* {
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			:root {
				--forest-dark: #1a2e1a;
				--forest-green: #2d5016;
				--moss-green: #4a7c2f;
				--leaf-green: #6b9d3a;
				--amber: #d4a257;
				--earth-brown: #5c4033;
				--cream: #f5f1e8;
				--text-light: #e8e4d8;
				--danger-red: #d84a4a;
			}

			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				color: var(--text-light);
				line-height: 1.7;
				min-height: 100vh;
			}

			.container {
				max-width: 900px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 2rem;
			}

			/* Navigation */
			.nav {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				padding: 1rem 0;
				position: sticky;
				top: 0;
				z-index: 100;
			}

			.nav .container {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: center;
				max-width: 1200px;
			}

			.logo {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 900;
				color: var(--amber);
				text-decoration: none;
				letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
			}

			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.nav-links a {
				color: var(--cream);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
				transition: color 0.3s;
			}

			.nav-links a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Breadcrumb */
			.breadcrumb {
				padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
			}

			.breadcrumb a {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.breadcrumb a:hover {
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Page Header */
			.page-header {
				padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
				text-align: center;
				border-bottom: 2px solid var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}

			.page-header h1 {
				font-size: 3rem;
				color: var(--amber);
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.subtitle {
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-style: italic;
			}

			/* Content */
			.content {
				padding-bottom: 4rem;
			}

			.rule-section {
				background: var(--forest-green);
				padding: 2rem;
				border-radius: 12px;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.rule-section.highlight {
				border-color: var(--amber);
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest-green) 0%, var(--moss-green) 100%);
			}

			.rule-section.danger {
				border-color: var(--danger-red);
			}

			.rule-section h2 {
				color: var(--amber);
				font-size: 1.75rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.rule-section h3 {
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-size: 1.25rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
			}

			.rule-section ul {
				margin-left: 1.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}

			.rule-section li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.key-points {
				list-style: none;
				margin-left: 0;
			}

			.key-points li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
			}

			.key-points li::before {
				content: "‚ö°";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
			}

			/* Action Blocks */
			.action-block {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin: 1rem 0;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
			}

			.action-block h3 {
				margin-top: 0;
			}

			/* Callout */
			.callout {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}

			.callout.danger {
				border-left-color: var(--danger-red);
			}

			.callout p {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}

			.callout p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			/* Formula */
			.formula {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin: 1rem 0;
				border: 2px solid var(--amber);
			}

			/* Recovery Box */
			.recovery-box {
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin: 1rem 0;
				border: 2px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.recovery-box.breathing {
				border-color: var(--leaf-green);
			}

			.recovery-box h3 {
				margin-top: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Table */
			.cost-table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
				margin: 1rem 0;
				background: var(--forest-dark);
				border-radius: 8px;
				overflow: hidden;
			}

			.cost-table th,
			.cost-table td {
				padding: 1rem;
				text-align: left;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--earth-brown);
			}

			.cost-table th {
				background: var(--moss-green);
				color: var(--amber);
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			.cost-table tr:last-child td {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.cost-table td:last-child {
				text-align: right;
				font-weight: 600;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Lists */
			.danger-list li {
				color: #ff9999;
			}

			.rhythm-list {
				list-style: none;
				margin-left: 0;
			}

			.rhythm-list li {
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
				position: relative;
			}

			.rhythm-list li::before {
				content: "‚Üí";
				position: absolute;
				left: 0;
				color: var(--amber);
			}

			/* Note */
			.note {
				font-style: italic;
				color: var(--leaf-green);
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}

			/* Responsive */
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.nav .container {
					flex-direction: column;
					gap: 1rem;
				}

				.nav-links {
					gap: 1rem;
					flex-wrap: wrap;
					justify-content: center;
				}

				.page-header h1 {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}

				.rule-section {
					padding: 1.5rem;
				}

				.cost-table th,
				.cost-table td {
					padding: 0.75rem;
					font-size: 0.9rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
